      "text": [
        " رِوَايَةِ جَمِيلٍ أَنَّهُ قَالَ : «غُسْلُ يَوْمِكَ يُجْزِيكَ لِلَيْلَتِكَ وَ غُسْلُ لَيْلَتِكَ يُجْزِيكَ لِيَوْمِكَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2542 - In a narration by Jamil, Imam (as) said:\n\"The ghusl of your day suffices for your night, and the ghusl of your night suffices for your day.\""
        ]
      }
